<A>__{ben takes off his coat and joins the kids in the living room. he hands over the present to his son. daisy is sitting in the armchair, holding her cat, tiger, in her arms.}
<C>__{ben }
<D>__{happy birthday, michael.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{what is it?}
