<D>__{duh, open it stupid!}
<A>__{michael tears away the wrapping paper and discovers a remote control car. the little boy is on cloud nine. later in the afternoon through the front window, we see a volvo station wagon park in front of the house. amy gets out of the car, loaded with shopping bags. she enters the house and hands the groceries over to rosa.}
<C>__{amy}
<D>__{hi rosa... where are the kids?}
<C>__{rosa}
<D>__{upstairs...}
